==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cowboy
<hw>Cow"boy`</hw> <pr>(-boi`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
cattle herder; a drover; specifically, one of an adventurous class of
herders and drovers on the plains of the Western and Southwestern United
States.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One of the marauders who, in the Revolutionary War
infested the neutral ground between the American and British lines, and
committed depredations on the Americans.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cowcatcher</ent>⟦br⟧
